                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-951513836" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-951513836" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="951513836">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/baicaitai/">Bear Ki</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-08-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">有点意思。1、“是非对错”不过是政治斗争中各方的兴衰晴雨表。2、我大明朝的问题一向都是“体制问题”。3、读史最令人感叹的不是历史总在重演，而是人性从未改变。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1171774281">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1171774281" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1171774281" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1171774281">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/seven117/">超立方蛤体</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-04-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">严谨并好读，非常喜欢这种完全不带节奏的断代史科普本</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

